headline: Modelo and Corona are unexpected casualties of Trump’s immigration crackdown
summary: Constellation Brands, the US owner of Modelo Especial and Corona, bet big on Latino customers for growth. But that strategy is unraveling under the Trump administration’s mass deportation push.

headline: Is Constellation Brands Stock Underperforming the S&P 500?
